What did you do to her?

7
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:47,933
Hey! Darn it!

8
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,866
So, where the heck did she go?

9
00:03:07,733 --> 00:03:08,933
Hey, look up there!

10
00:03:09,266 --> 00:03:11,066
Do you see her?

11
00:03:15,633 --> 00:03:17,166
Hey, look at that!

12
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:28,900
Chi! Where'd you go, Chi?!
Answer me!

13
00:03:29,366 --> 00:03:30,800
Where did she go?

14
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,433
Huh?

15
00:04:01,866 --> 00:04:03,733
Now how on earth could
a thing like that happen?

16
00:04:04,066 --> 00:04:06,000
Yuzuki, replay at
1/4 speed for me!

17
00:04:06,066 --> 00:04:07,366
Right.

18
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:24,133
Yuzuki!

19
00:04:26,133 --> 00:04:27,466
Yuzuki!

20
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:31,966
Darn it. Where is she?

21
00:04:36,433 --> 00:04:38,933
Sumomo, we've gotta get
a hold of Minoru right now!

22
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,333
Can you try calling him at home?

23
00:04:42,133 --> 00:04:43,533
Huh? Hey, Sumomo.

24
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,500
What's wrong? Are you all right?

25
00:04:45,566 --> 00:04:47,433
Sumomo! Sumomo!

26
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:49,066
No way, she can't be broken!

27
00:04:49,133 --> 00:04:50,800
Say something, Sumomo!

28
00:04:51,333 --> 00:04:52,100
Darn it.

29
00:04:52,166 --> 00:04:53,700
And just when
I borrowed her, too.

30
00:04:53,766 --> 00:04:55,433
