of the train station.

39
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:11,466
All of you who've
stopped your Persocoms

40
00:05:11,533 --> 00:05:14,233
in the courtyard in
front of the train station,

41
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,566
please move them immediately!

42
00:05:15,633 --> 00:05:17,900
You are impeding
the flow of traffic.

43
00:05:17,966 --> 00:05:20,800
Please get them
cleared away immediately.

44
00:05:20,866 --> 00:05:24,200
Hey, what's going on?
Is ours working?

45
00:05:24,266 --> 00:05:25,200
Naw, it's down.

46
00:05:25,266 --> 00:05:26,700
Can't seem to
figure it out, either.

47
00:05:26,766 --> 00:05:28,433
