50
00:05:31,866 --> 00:05:34,766
I'd like to know just
what the hell's going on.

51
00:05:34,833 --> 00:05:38,766
What's up? Did something happen?

52
00:05:38,833 --> 00:05:40,600
So it's not moving
at all then, is it?

53
00:05:40,666 --> 00:05:41,933
Uh, no.

54
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,433
I don't suppose you have any
idea how all of this happened?

55
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:46,300
Well just before,
when it was looking up

56
00:05:46,366 --> 00:05:48,633
at the Persocom standing
on top of the clock,

57
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,466
it suddenly stopped moving.

58
00:05:50,533 --> 00:05:52,466
Clock? Persocom?

59
00:05:59,133 --> 00:06:01,966
Hmm? Well there isn't
anything like that around here.

60
00:06:02,033 --> 00:06:03,400
Uh, yeah...

61
00:06:03,466 --> 00:06:04,933
Chi, where are you?!

62
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:07,633
Come on, where are you? Chi!

63
00:06:33,133 --> 00:06:34,066
Chi!

64
00:06:40,433 --> 00:06:41,566
Chi!

65
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,133
Chi!

66
00:06:51,766 --> 00:06:53,933
