to find a place that perfect.

202
00:14:16,100 --> 00:14:17,600
Please don't be
worried about last night.

203
00:14:17,666 --> 00:14:19,233
I didn't take
offense or anything.

204
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:20,500
Yeah, well that's good,

205
00:14:20,566 --> 00:14:23,300
but I was really looking forward
to your home-cooked meal, Yumi.

206
00:14:23,366 --> 00:14:24,366
Anyway, as it turned out,

207
00:14:24,433 --> 00:14:26,533
it was a good thing your
Persocom was all right.

208
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,900
Yeah, that's true.

209
00:14:27,966 --> 00:14:30,500
But she still doesn't
understand what she did.

210
00:14:30,566 --> 00:14:32,166
And I think she
just might be liable

211
00:14:32,233 --> 00:14:33,633
to do something strange again,

212
00:14:33,700 --> 00:14:36,966
