to find her a new job.

213
00:14:37,033 --> 00:14:38,600
Oh I see.

214
00:14:38,666 --> 00:14:40,166
I bet that won't very easy.

215
00:14:40,233 --> 00:14:43,366
Well, actually,
it was pretty tough,

216
00:14:43,433 --> 00:14:44,766
but I finally found one.

217
00:14:44,833 --> 00:14:46,000
Huh?

218
00:14:46,066 --> 00:14:47,933
A job for my Persocom.

219
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,666
It's a bakery right
here in the mall.

220
00:14:49,733 --> 00:14:51,466
I'm sure you must've
seen it at some point.

221
00:14:51,533 --> 00:14:52,833
It's a place called Tirol.

222
00:14:52,900 --> 00:14:53,900
And as luck would have it,

223
00:14:53,966 --> 00:14:55,466
