of festival at the moment,

224
00:14:55,533 --> 00:14:58,033
which sounded like
just the thing to me.

225
00:14:58,100 --> 00:14:59,100
Anniversary...

226
00:14:59,166 --> 00:15:00,233
Huh?

227
00:15:00,300 --> 00:15:02,933
It's their 5th anniversary
festival, right?

228
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,266
It says it right here.

229
00:15:04,333 --> 00:15:05,866
That's what the
flyer's all about.

230
00:15:05,933 --> 00:15:07,666
Yeah, that's right!

231
00:15:07,733 --> 00:15:10,266
So I talked to the owner
about it, he was very nice,

232
00:15:10,333 --> 00:15:12,133
and he said he'd
be happy to hire Chi!

233
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,866
Man, I'm so relieved.

234
00:15:13,933 --> 00:15:16,200
I was thinking I'd never
be able to find something.

235
00:15:16,266 --> 00:15:20,766
That's so great.
You sure are lucky!

236
00:15:20,833 --> 00:15:23,000
Okay, everybody,
time to open up.

237
00:15:23,066 --> 00:15:25,033
My Pleasure!

238
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:25,733
Ready, Yumi?

239
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:26,933
Sure!

240
00:15:36,766 --> 00:15:37,933
Come on in.

241
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:41,733
Everyone's welcome to Tirol
Bakery's fifth anniversary fair.

242
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:44,400
Treat yourself
and join us inside.

243
00:15:44,466 --> 00:15:47,933
Free gifts and prizes for
everyone who buys pastries.

