00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:06,000
Yeah, of course.
Take a look at the ears.

251
00:16:06,066 --> 00:16:07,300
It's a dead give-away.

252
00:16:07,366 --> 00:16:09,366
Oh wow, well,
she's still really cute!

253
00:16:09,433 --> 00:16:10,866
So, is that a
